calculateCollateral(address,uint256,uint.details: calculates the total collateral price of the NFT. Imagine virtual museums that rent out the NFTs of the artists for some time. Therefore, there is a potential for reputation here. If the borrower has consistently good renting track-record, they will get more favourable quotes

params._duration: number of days that the user wishes to rent out the NFT for. 1 means 1 day

returns._0: the total collateral + fee the borrower has to put up*
